{"tid":832805,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城主席揭露點解唔簽山齊士！（山神）","createTime":"2018-09-23T05:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T18:47:00.000Z","uid":119778,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ba0569e50bd985688310bf7125a726e131b6f581","tid":832805,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:05:29.000Z","msg":"近日，曼城隊紀錄片《All or nothing》正在熱映，而在該紀錄片中，曼城主席也就球隊為何不簽入前阿仙奴球員山齊士作出回應，原因竟然只是單純覺得山齊士太貴了！<br />\n　　<br />\n曼城主席穆波歷克表示：「事實上，哥迪奧拿非常欣賞山齊士，我們在2017年就想把他帶到曼城，但那時的形勢不太好。在一月我們又嘗試與山齊士進行接觸，<span style=\"color: red;\">但是超過4,000萬英鎊的轉會費，加上球員每週50萬英鎊的工資，這實在太貴了！</span>沒有其他原因，就是因為這個，我們沒有簽山齊士&middot;&middot;&middot;」<br />\n<br />\n最終的結果是，山齊士選擇加盟曼城的同城死敵曼聯，在19場比賽中攻入3球。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曼城主席酸能到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一邊用小米一邊厭iPhone貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd803e5bb141f5dd21857addf863a140700313c8","tid":832805,"uid":16343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:30:56.000Z","msg":"意思係佢唔值依個價姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實證明係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94964e7e85dca5e25a8a0af7c919ee24b9a886b6","tid":832805,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"仲"},{"pid":"408bc74bc9c3be223290fcb82818fa7fc4d6d31c","tid":832805,"uid":20473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"94964e7e85dca5e25a8a0af7c919ee24b9a886b6","tid":832805,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"仲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:35:51.000Z","msg":"鏝城收五十萬 去獌聯梗係做義工"},{"pid":"94bb5aa7e3aab5887840fafc114fee2b30019729","tid":832805,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd803e5bb141f5dd21857addf863a140700313c8","tid":832805,"uid":16343,"like"